        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple Watch 被指有「误触」情况，外媒：Apple 内部文件承认问题</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/apple-watch-touch-issue/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-watch-touch-issue</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/apple-watch-touch-issue/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 10:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手机配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple watch]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229059</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前有 Apple Watch 用户发现，手表出现无故误触情况。在没有触碰手表荧幕的情况下，手机画面被不规则的自动按动，有用户的手表更被自动输入密码，被回报「密码错误，请 3 小时后再试」。有消息指 Apple 向授权维修供应商提醒不要为出现此状况的用户更换手表，而是建议用户等待下一次软件更新。</p><p>根据报道，早在 2 月时 Apple 已向授权维修供应商提到 Apple Watch 误触情况，问题影响 Apple Watch Series 9、Apple Watch Ultra 2。其后有报告指灾情扩展到 Apple Watch Series 7, 8，以及第一代 Apple Watch Ultra。报道指，Apple 提醒授权维修商不要因此问题而为用户更换手表，只需向用户提示按住 Apple Watch 上两个按钮 10 秒钟来强制重新启动手表便可，并确保手表维持在最新的 watchOS。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">This has JUST been extended to series 7, series 8, as well as ultra 1 just FYI</p><p>Apple has advised us not to replace watches for this issue and to tell people to basically force restart the watch by holding both buttons together for 10 seconds and also keep your watches up-to-date <a href="https://t.co/klrVeYhkD0">https://t.co/klrVeYhkD0</a></p><p>&mdash; Stella &#8211; Fudge (@StellaFudge) <a href="https://twitter.com/StellaFudge/status/1778197004029394994?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 10, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>早前有用户指 Apple Watch 无故被触动的情况，令他们难于使用手表，有些人需要重新开机。而用户如遇到这种情况，可留意最新版 watchOS 更新。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_58536"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/m9OJDSIyu3M?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://technews.tw/2024/04/12/apple-watch-ghosttouches/">TechNews.tw</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/01/apples-website-finally-has-tech-specs-pages-for-apple-watch-models/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Watch 官网终于展示技术规格　之前未有个别展示详细规格</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/apple-watch-consider-support-android/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 回应美国司法部垄断指控，曾研究 Apple Watch 支援 Android 手机</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/05/hermes-apple-watch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全新 Hermès Apple Watch 表带登场，与其他系列共新增 22 款</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/apple-watch-touch-issue/mobile-phone/phone-parts/">Apple Watch 被指有「误触」情况，外媒：Apple 内部文件承认问题</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
