        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 电车到港，双色系型格车身、超豪内笼抢先睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/mercedes-maybach-eqs-680-suv/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mercedes-maybach-eqs-680-suv</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/mercedes-maybach-eqs-680-suv/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 07:00:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes-Maybach]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229022</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Maybach 品牌的首款全电动车款 Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 近日正式到港。日前就在商场举办活动，就等小编一齐同大家去睇睇新车各种设计。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229025" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123213-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123213-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123213.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229026" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123240-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123240-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123240.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 车头设有经典的黑色面板和垂直的镀铬装饰条，突显出立体外观轮廓。引擎盖上镶嵌著平治星型标志，黑色的大型面板则首次以闭合方式设计。车身侧面突显了镀铬边框和镀铬的 B 柱装饰，后排座椅区域长度由此突出。车尾则装饰有连续式灯带和镀铬装饰元素，增添了更型格外观。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1233110-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1233110-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1233110.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229028" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123330-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123330-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123330.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229029" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1500130-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1500130-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1500130.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229030" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150640-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150640-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在动力规格方面，这款 SUV 搭载了先进全电动驱动系统，续航距离最大为 635 公里，输出功率达 484 千瓦，扭力达 950 牛顿米。4MATIC 全轮驱动系统为标准设备。在快速充电站以直流电充电 15 分钟后，最高可获得 220 公里续航距离。而透过封装的前后电动驱动系统和创新的前轴支撑架，进一步提升了驾驶的稳定性和舒适性。Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 最高速度为 210 km/h，0-100 km/h 加速度为 4.4 秒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150720-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150720-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150720.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车厢设计结合了传统与前衞的元素，采用了 Maybach 的设计理念「What is good must also be beautiful」。车厢中，前排乘客可以使用标准配备的 MBUX Hyberscreen 屏幕，所有三个显示屏均展示 Mercedes-Maybach 特定的启动动画和专属功能。在电子系统方面，车载配有 MBUX 娱乐资讯系统，提供前后座独立控制的多功能显示屏，并支持丰富的定制选项。这包括三种显示风格（discreet、sporty、MAYBACH）和多种模式（navigation、assistance、service），以满足不同的使用需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229032" src="https: