ads/2024/04/20240412_150741.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229036" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151024-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151024-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151024.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151104-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151104-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151104.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151128-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151128-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151128.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>科技系统中，Mercedes-Maybach EQS SUV 配备了各种先进技术，包括自动门的开关控制、MBUX High-End Rear Seat Entertainment 系统以及具有 253 个可控 LED 和 64 种色调的主动式气氛灯，提供个性化的舒适体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151210-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151210-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151210.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px